ttern(0): WORD,    pad1(1): WORD,    cursorPosition(2): WORD,    pad3(3): WORD,    displayControl(4): WORD];  END.LOG 9-May-89 - JPM - Created. 5-Jun-89 - JPM - Modified per new hardware spec. 9-Jan-90 - JPM - Added new DisplayType variant and screen size parameters.21-Aug-90 - JPM - Added DisplayAddressControl.